::Prowl::

Prowl speeds up, the shots hitting his feet. He clenches his teeth at the 
jolts of pain coming from that area. He activates his comm-link.

"Any Maximals," he says into it, "This is Prowl. Me and Dinobot got Iron and 
Tav out of the Alliance base. They're chasing us right now, along with half 
the preds! Any help would be apreciated!"
